9b71			; the core word dictionary v4 
9b71			; https://www.complang.tuwien.ac.at/forth/gforth/Docs-html/Notation.html#Notation 
9b71			 
9b71			; this is a linked list for each of the system words used 
9b71			; user defined words will follow the same format but will be in ram 
9b71			 
9b71			 
9b71			; 
9b71			; 
9b71			; define linked list: 
9b71			; 
9b71			; 1. compiled byte op code 
9b71			; 2. len of text word 
9b71			; 3. text word 
9b71			; 4. ptr to next dictionary word 
9b71			; 5. asm, calls etc for the word 
9b71			; 
9b71			;  if 1 == 0 then last word in dict  
9b71			;   
9b71			; set the start of dictionary scanning to be in ram and the last word point to the system dict 
9b71			;  
