baae			; | SYMBOL ( u1 -- )  Get the address of a system symbol from a look up table to TOS  | DONE 
baae			; | 
baae			; | | The value is the number reference and the final address is pushed to stack 
baae			 
baae			; | | ``` 
baae			; | | dw sym_table 
baae			; | | dw nmi_vector 
baae			; | | dw cli_autodisplay 
baae			; | | dw cli_data_sp 
baae			; | | dw cli_data_stack 
baae			; | | dw cli_loop_sp 
baae			; | | dw cli_loop_stack 
