bbce			.SPIO: 
bbce			 
bbce			if STORAGE_SE 
bbce				CWHEAD .SPICEH 61 "SPICEL" 6 WORD_FLAG_CODE 
bbce			; | SPICEL ( -- ) Set SPI CE low for the currently selected device |  DONE 
bbce			 
